caption: ⚡ In the rain-soaked neon district of Neo-Tokyo, Liora Vex, a cyberpunk femme fat, slinks through flickering streets, her holographic dress cutting the night's pulse. 💜 She laces her high-slit boots, capturing every glimmer of the city, and the camera hones in on her silhouette as she rides the electric wind. #cyberpunk #neoncity #streetfashion #digitalart #neon
